        "## BERT vs Gen AI: Sentiment Analysis of Women's E-commerce Clothing Reviews {.project-main-title}\n",
        "\n",
        "<p class=\"project-meta\">MSc Business Analytics · NLP & Sentiment Analysis · Ariane Damian · Apr. 17, 2026</p>\n",
